<config xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:magento:module:Magento_Config:etc/system_file.xsd">
    <system>
        <section id="payment">
            <group id="paypal_br" sortOrder="6" showInDefault="0" showInWebsite="0" showInStore="0">
            	<group id="paypal_plus" translate="label comment" type="text" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
            		<label>PayPal Plus</label>
            		<comment>A experiência de um checkout transparente processado com a segurança do PayPal. O usuário efetua o pagamento diretamente em seu site, sem a necessidade de criar uma conta, utilizando apenas o cartão de crédito.</comment>
            		<fieldset_css>complex paypalbr-section</fieldset_css>
            		<frontend_model>Magento\Paypal\Block\Adminhtml\System\Config\Fieldset\Payment</frontend_model>
            		<attribute type="activity_path">payment/paypal_plus/active</attribute>
                    <attribute type="displayIn">recommended_solutions</attribute>
                    <field id="active" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Enable this Solution</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/active</config_path>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                    </field>
                    <field id="exibition_name" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Exibition Name</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/exibition_name</config_path>
                        <comment>Será exibido no checkout: Cartão de Crédito (Parcelado em 12x)</comment>
                        <tooltip>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</tooltip>
                    </field>
                    <field id="mode" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Mode</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/mode</config_path>
                        <source_model>PayPalBR\PayPalPlus\Model\Config\Source\Mode</source_model>
                        <comment>Utilize essa opção para alternar entre modos SandBox e Produção. SandBox é utilizado para testes e Produção para compras reais.</comment>
                    </field>
                    <field id="client_id_sandbox" translate="label" type="password" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Client ID SandBox</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/client_id_sandbox</config_path>
                        <comment><![CDATA[Para gerar o Client ID acesse <a href="#">aqui</a> e procure pela seção "REST API Apps".]]></comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="mode">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                    <field id="secret_id_sandbox" translate="label" type="password" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Secret ID SandBox</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/secret_id_sandbox</config_path>
                        <comment><![CDATA[Para gerar o Secret ID acesse <a href="#">aqui</a> e procure pela seção "REST API Apps".]]></comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="mode">1</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                    <field id="client_id_production" translate="label" type="password" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Client ID Production</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/client_id_production</config_path>
                        <comment><![CDATA[Para gerar o Client ID acesse <a href="#">aqui</a> e procure pela seção "REST API Apps".]]></comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="mode">2</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                    <field id="secret_id_production" translate="label" type="password" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Secret ID Production</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/secret_id_production</config_path>
                        <comment><![CDATA[Para gerar o Secret ID acesse <a href="#">aqui</a> e procure pela seção "REST API Apps".]]></comment>
                        <depends>
                            <field id="mode">2</field>
                        </depends>
                    </field>
                    <field id="payment_action" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Payment Action</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/secret_id_sandbox</config_path>
                        <source_model>PayPalBR\PayPalPlus\Model\Config\Source\PaymentAction</source_model>
                    </field>
                    <field id="new_order_status" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>New Order Status</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/new_order_status</config_path>
                    </field>
                    <field id="depuration_mode" translate="label" type="select" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Depuration Mode</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/depuration_mode</config_path>
                        <source_model>Magento\Config\Model\Config\Source\Yesno</source_model>
                        <comment><![CDATA[Os logs serão salvos no caminho: <a href="#">X > Y</a>]]></comment>
                        <tooltip>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.</tooltip>
                    </field>
                    <field id="sort_order" translate="label" type="text" sortOrder="0" showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="0">
                        <label>Sort Order</label>
                        <config_path>payment/paypal_plus/sort_order</config_path>
                    </field>
            	</group>
            </group>
        </section>
    </system>
</config>
